stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_type: validate transaction
    q_check_type --> q_error_type: unknown transaction type
    q_check_type --> q_check_contract: known transaction type
    q_error_type --> [*]: raise TransactionTypeError
    q_check_contract --> q_error_contract: type disallows contract creation AND to == None
    q_check_contract --> q_check_fee: contract creation allowed OR to != None
    q_error_contract --> [*]: raise TransactionTypeContractCreationError
    q_check_fee --> q_error_fee: max_fee_per_gas less than base_fee_per_gas
    q_check_fee --> q_check_priority: max_fee_per_gas >= base_fee_per_gas
    q_error_fee --> [*]: raise InsufficientMaxFeePerGasError
    q_check_priority --> q_error_priority: priority_fee greater than max_fee
    q_check_priority --> q_check_gas_limit: priority_fee <= max_fee
    q_error_priority --> [*]: raise PriorityFeeGreaterThanMaxFeeError
    q_check_gas_limit --> q_error_gas: gas_limit exceeds maximum
    q_check_gas_limit --> q_check_initcode: gas_limit within maximum
    q_error_gas --> [*]: raise TransactionGasLimitExceededError
    q_check_initcode --> q_error_initcode: init_code too large
    q_check_initcode --> q_check_blob: init_code within limit
    q_error_initcode --> [*]: raise InitCodeTooLargeError
    q_check_blob --> q_valid: not blob transaction
    q_check_blob --> q_check_blob_detail: is blob transaction
    q_valid --> [*]: transaction valid
    q_check_blob_detail --> q_error_no_blob: no blob data
    q_check_blob_detail --> q_check_blob_count: has blob data
    q_error_no_blob --> [*]: raise NoBlobDataError
    q_check_blob_count --> q_error_blob_count: blob count exceeds limit
    q_check_blob_count --> q_check_blob_gas: blob count within limit
    q_error_blob_count --> [*]: raise BlobCountExceededError
    q_check_blob_gas --> q_error_blob_gas: blob gas limit exceeded
    q_check_blob_gas --> q_check_blob_fee: blob gas within limit
    q_error_blob_gas --> [*]: raise BlobGasLimitExceededError
    q_check_blob_fee --> q_error_blob_fee: max_fee_per_blob_gas insufficient
    q_check_blob_fee --> q_check_blob_hash: max_fee_per_blob_gas sufficient
    q_error_blob_fee --> [*]: raise InsufficientMaxFeePerBlobGasError
    q_check_blob_hash --> q_error_blob_hash: invalid blob versioned hash
    q_check_blob_hash --> q_check_auth: valid blob versioned hash
    q_error_blob_hash --> [*]: raise InvalidBlobVersionedHashError
    q_check_auth --> q_error_auth: empty authorization list
    q_check_auth --> q_valid2: authorization list valid or not applicable
    q_error_auth --> [*]: raise EmptyAuthorizationListError
    q_valid2 --> [*]: transaction valid
